# vhs tape for the README demo GIF. Replays the captured output of
# examples/demo_invalidity_chart.py (real output; timing synthetic — see
# scripts/replay_demo.py). Regenerate with:  vhs docs/assets/demo.tape
Output docs/assets/demo.gif
Set FontSize 13
Set Width 1100
Set Height 640
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 12
Set Framerate 12
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Hide
Type "cd ~/patentkit && clear && .venv/bin/python scripts/replay_demo.py docs/assets/demo_replay.log 120"
Enter
Show
Sleep 30s
